description:
Tentacles Coin (CLES) is the native currency of the Tentacles Evolution branch of the EcoSysten – EcoPlanetar ecosystem.
The project combines AI, Meme, NFT and active digital energy, creating a living network of interconnected coins and NFTs.
Tentacles Coin represents “digital energy in motion” – a decentralized system that transforms the idea of ​​currency into an evolutionary form of collective consciousness and energy balance.
CLES has the role of supporting exchanges, staking and transactions between the EcoPlanetar and Tentacles branches, being the connecting element between innovation, digital art and decentralized finance.
By integrating into the MultiversX ecosystem, CLES becomes a symbol of the transition to an organic and intelligent digital economy.
